
:tabedit <filename>

:tabn,:tabp -- navigating across tab

:gt -- go to next tab 

:gT -- go to previous tab 

:3gt -- got the 3rd tab in next 


 ***** keyboard shotct 


ctrl + page up/down

:tabnew --- to open new tab 

:w <filename> -- to name the new file opened in the tab 
:tabm 

	:tabm 0 -- move the current tab to first position / far left
	:tabm 4 -- move the current tab to 4th position from left 



:q -- close current tab 
:tabclose -- close current tab

:tab ball -- to open all the files in buffer / all the files we are working with recently

:set tabpagemax = 10;


:tabonly -- close all the tabs expect the current one 

:tabclose 3 -- close 3rd tab 


:drop <file-name> closes the current file and open the file specified 

:split / :sp  -- split the window 


how to open one of the split window into new tab 

:tab split

ctrl + wT

